# Skill: Chuc Nang Moi - Tao Module Tu A-Z

## Muc dich
Skill nay giup tao mot chuc nang moi tu dau khi chua co skill rieng cho module do

## Khi nao su dung

Su dung skill nay khi:
- Can tao module hoan toan moi (vi du: vendors, inventory, reports)
- Module chua co skill rieng trong `skills/`
- Can xay dung tu A-Z: docs, backend, frontend

## Workflow 7 Buoc

### Buoc 1: Thu thap thong tin
- Xac dinh yeu cau tu user (CRUD, report, feature moi)
- Hoi user ve:
  - Ten module (vi du: "vendors" - Nha cung cap)
  - Muc dich chuc nang
  - Cac truong du lieu chinh
  - Cac thao tac can co (Create, Read, Update, Delete, Import, Export?)
- Validate input dau vao

### Buoc 2: Kiem tra ton tai
- Kiem tra `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md` xem module da co chua
- Kiem tra `skills/` xem da co skill cho module chua
- Kiem tra `docs/` xem da co docs chua
- Kiem tra codebase xem da co files nao lien quan chua

### Buoc 3: Lap ke hoach tao moi

**Neu module chua ton tai:**
- [ ] Tao docs/<ten-module>.md
- [ ] Tao Backend: Model, Controller, Service, Routes
- [ ] Tao Frontend: Component, Types
- [ ] Dinh nghia Permissions
- [ ] Tao skill/<ten-module>.skill

**Neu module da ton tai mot phan:**
- [ ] Bo sung files con thieu
- [ ] Cap nhat docs
- [ ] Cap nhat skill (neu co)

### Buoc 4: Tao tai lieu truoc
- **Tao docs/<ten-module>.md TRUOC TIEN**
- Su dung `docs/TEMPLATE.md` lam mau
- Dinh nghia:
  - Tong quan module
  - Database schema
  - API endpoints
  - Frontend components
  - Permissions
  - Luồng nghiep vu

### Buoc 5: Thuc thi Backend
- Tao Model: `backend/app/Models/<Model>.php`
- Tao Controller: `backend/app/Http/Controllers/<Controller>Controller.php`
- Tao Service: `backend/app/Services/V5/Domain/<Domain>Service.php`
- Them Routes: `backend/routes/api.php`
- Tao migration (neu can): `backend/database/migrations/`

### Buoc 6: Thuc thi Frontend
- Tao Component: `frontend/components/<Component>.tsx`
- Them types: `frontend/types.ts`
- Them API calls: `frontend/services/v5Api.ts`
- Tao Modal/Forms (neu can)

### Buoc 7: Hoan thien va ban giao
- Chay test/lint
- Chay skill `init-he-thong.skill` de cap nhat `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md`
- **Tao skill/<ten-module>.skill** voi thong tin:
  - Workflow 5 buoc
  - Files lien quan
  - Permissions
  - Tab ID
- Cap nhat `skills/README.md` voi skill moi
- Ban giao cho user

---

## Template Ke Hoach

```markdown
# Ke hoach tao module <Ten-Module>

## Tong quan
- **Ten module**: <ten>
- **Muc dich**: <mo ta>
- **Nguoi dung**: <ai su dung>

## Database
- **Bang chinh**: <ten_bang>
- **Truong chinh**:
  - id (primary key)
  - <field1> - <kieu du lieu>
  - <field2> - <kieu du lieu>

## Backend
- **Model**: <Model>.php
- **Controller**: <Controller>Controller.php
- **Service**: <Domain>Service.php
- **Routes**: /api/v5/<module>

## Frontend
- **Component**: <Component>.tsx
- **Tab ID**: <tab_id>
- **Permissions**: <module>.read, <module>.write

## Timeline
1. Tao docs - 30 phut
2. Tao Backend - 1-2 gio
3. Tao Frontend - 1-2 gio
4. Test va ban giao - 30 phut
```

---

## Vi Du Su Dung

### Vi du 1: Tao module Vendors

```
User: "Can tao module quan ly nha cung cap (vendors)"

Skill chuc-nang-moi se:
1. Hoi thong tin: truong du lieu, thao tac can co
2. Kiem tra xem vendors da co chua
3. Len ke hoach tao tu A-Z
4. Tao docs/vendors.md
5. Tao Backend: Vendor.php, VendorController.php, VendorDomainService.php
6. Tao Frontend: VendorList.tsx, VendorModal.tsx
7. Tao skill/vendors.skill
8. Chay init-he-thong
```

### Vi du 2: Them chuc nang vao module existing

```
User: "Them chuc nang export Excel vao module contracts"

Skill chuc-nang-moi se:
1. Kiem tra contracts da co skill chua
2. Doc docs/contracts.md
3. Them endpoint export vao Controller
4. Them nut Export vao Frontend
5. Cap nhat docs/contracts.md
6. Cap nhat skills/contracts.skill
7. Chay init-he-thong
```

---

## Checklist Khi Tao Module Moi

### Tai lieu
- [ ] docs/<ten-module>.md
- [ ] skills/<ten-module>.skill
- [ ] skills/README.md (cap nhat)

### Backend
- [ ] Model
- [ ] Controller
- [ ] Service (DomainService)
- [ ] Routes
- [ ] Migration (neu can)
- [ ] Seeder (neu can)
- [ ] Tests

### Frontend
- [ ] Component chinh (List)
- [ ] Modal (Form)
- [ ] Types
- [ ] API calls
- [ ] Hooks (neu can)

### Permissions
- [ ] Dinh nghia permissions
- [ ] Gan vao routes
- [ ] Cap nhat frontend

### Audit
- [ ] Audit logs
- [ ] init-he-thong

---

## Tham chieu

- `CLAUDE.md` - Project conventions
- `GIT_RULES_WORKFLOWS.md` - Git workflow
- `init-he-thong.skill` - Setup guide
- `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md` - Codebase overview
- `docs/TEMPLATE.md` - Mau tai lieu
- `skills/template/SKILL.md` - Mau skill

---

## Luu y

1. **Luon tao docs TRUOC** - De hieu ro module truoc khi code
2. **Su dung DomainService pattern** - Nhu cac module khac
3. **Tuan thu conventions** - React 19, Laravel 11, TypeScript
4. **Test sau moi buoc** - Dam bao hoat dong dung
5. **Cap nhat skill sau cung** - Khi da xong het

---

## Cauhinh nhanh

Neu can tao nhanh skill cho module moi, copy template nay:

```markdown
# Skill: <Ten> - <Mo Ta>

## Muc dich
Skill nay giup doc docs va code nhanh cho module <Ten>

## Workflow 5 Buoc
( nhu tren )

## Files lien quan
### Backend
- Models: backend/app/Models/<Model>.php
- Controllers: backend/app/Http/Controllers/<Controller>Controller.php
- Routes: backend/routes/api.php
- Services: backend/app/Services/V5/Domain/<Domain>Service.php

### Frontend
- Components: frontend/components/<Component>.tsx
- Services: frontend/services/v5Api.ts
- Types: frontend/types.ts

### Docs
- `docs/<ten>.md`

## Permissions
- <module>.read, <module>.write, <module>.delete

## Tab ID
- <tab_id>
```
